<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Service Suspended - XSpaceGrow</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c757d 0%, #495057 100%); color: white; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
    .suspension-box { background-color: #f8d7da; border: 2px solid #dc3545; color: #721c24; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; margin: 15px 0; }
    .cta-button:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3); }
    .impact-details { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #6c757d; }
    .grace-info { background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; color: #856404; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
    .suspended-badge { background-color: #6c757d; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; }
    .data-warning { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeaa7 0%, #fab1a0 100%); padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 20px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üîí Service Suspended</h1>
      <p>Your XSpaceGrow account requires immediate attention</p>
      <div class="suspended-badge">
        SERVICE TEMPORARILY SUSPENDED
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.first_name || @user.email.split('@').first.titleize %>,</p>

      <p>We regret to inform you that your XSpaceGrow <%= @plan.name %> plan has been temporarily suspended due to <%= @suspension_reason.downcase %>. Your IoT devices and monitoring services are currently inactive.</p>

      <!-- Suspension Details -->
      <div class="suspension-box">
        <h3>üö® Suspension Details</h3>
        <ul style="margin: 15px 0;">
          <li><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= @suspension_reason %></li>
          <li><strong>Suspended Devices:</strong> <%= @suspended_devices_count %> devices affected</li>
          <li><strong>Grace Period:</strong> <%= @grace_period_days %> days to reactivate</li>
          <li><strong>Action Required:</strong> Update payment information</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Data Protection Warning -->
      <div class="data-warning">
        <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Data Protection Notice</h3>
        <p><strong>Your data is safe for <%= @grace_period_days %> days.</strong></p>
        <p>After <%= @permanent_suspension_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>, inactive accounts may have their data archived or deleted according to our data retention policy.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Service Impact -->
      <div class="impact-details">
        <h3>üìä Services Currently Affected</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>‚ùå Real-time device monitoring</li>
          <li>‚ùå Data collection from sensors</li>
          <li>‚ùå Alert notifications and warnings</li>
          <li>‚ùå Dashboard access and analytics</li>
          <li>‚ùå API integrations and exports</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Account access (for reactivation)</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Historical data (preserved for <%= @grace_period_days %> days)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Reactivation CTA -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <% if @can_reactivate_immediately %>
          <a href="<%= @reactivation_url %>" class="cta-button" style="color: white;">
            üîÑ Reactivate Service Now
          </a>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-top: 10px;">
            Instant reactivation available ‚Ä¢ Secure payment processing
          </p>
        <% else %>
          <a href="<%= @reactivation_url %>" class="cta-button" style="color: white;">
            üí≥ Update Payment Method
          </a>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-top: 10px;">
            Reactivation within 24 hours of payment update
          </p>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <!-- Grace Period Information -->
      <div class="grace-info">
        <h4>‚è≥ <%= @grace_period_days %>-Day Grace Period</h4>
        <p><strong>You have until <%= @permanent_suspension_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %> to reactivate your service.</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your devices will automatically reconnect upon reactivation</li>
          <li>Historical data remains intact and accessible</li>
          <li>All custom settings and configurations are preserved</li>
          <li>No setup or reconfiguration required</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- What Reactivation Includes -->
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h3>üöÄ Reactivation Restores Full Service</h3>
        <ul style="margin: 15px 0;">
          <li>‚úÖ All <%= @suspended_devices_count %> devices come back online</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Real-time monitoring resumes immediately</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Alert notifications reactivate</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Full dashboard and analytics access</li>
          <li>‚úÖ API integrations reconnect</li>
          <li>‚úÖ Priority support restoration</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Prevent Future Suspensions -->
      <div style="background-color: #e8f4f8; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h4>üí° Prevent Future Service Interruptions</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Auto-Pay:</strong> Enable automatic payments for seamless billing</li>
          <li><strong>Backup Payment:</strong> Add a secondary payment method</li>
          <li><strong>Billing Alerts:</strong> Get notified before payment issues occur</li>
          <li><strong>Account Monitoring:</strong> Regular billing email confirmations</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Support -->
      <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h4>Need Immediate Assistance? ü§ù</h4>
        <p>Our reactivation team is standing by:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>üî• <strong>Urgent Line:</strong> 1-800-XSPACE-1 (press 1 for reactivation)</li>
          <li>üìß <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:reactivation@xspacegrow.com">reactivation@xspacegrow.com</a></li>
          <li>üí¨ <strong>Live Chat:</strong> Available 24/7 in your account portal</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 15px;">
          <strong>Average reactivation time:</strong> 2-4 hours after payment resolution
        </p>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        We understand this suspension may be inconvenient. Our team is here to help restore your service as quickly as possible.<br><br>
        <strong>The XSpaceGrow Reactivation Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        XSpaceGrow ‚Ä¢ IoT Device Management Platform<br>
        <a href="<%= @reactivation_url %>">Reactivate Service</a> ‚Ä¢ 
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/support">Emergency Support</a>
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 15px;">
        Subscription ID: <%= @subscription.id %> ‚Ä¢ Suspension effective immediately
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>